description:
Here are ten PSP hidden gems that are often overlooked when talking about Sony's first handheld Playstation console. So many great games released for the system but a lot of the obscure and lesser known titles are still worth playing to this day. Let us know your list of top ten PSP hidden gems down below in the comments as we countdown ours!
